---
title: Pan-Seared Tofu and Orange Salad with Strawberry Vinaigrette
description: Tonight's dinner is a pop of bright, summery flavours with a strawberry vinaigrette that clings to juicy oranges and seared tofu. It's an instant boost of Vitamin C!
